msgid "anārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides, he commits "
"one offense entailing suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="86"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1502"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.31"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.32"
msgid "“kuṭiṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a hut and then departs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.33"
msgid "Tassa kuṭiṃ karonti pamāṇikaṃ sārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They build one which is within the size limit, where harm will be done, and "
"which lacks a space on all sides."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.34"
msgid ""
"So ce vippakate āgacchati, tena bhikkhunā sā kuṭi aññassa vā dātabbā "
"bhinditvā vā puna kātabbā."
msgstr ""
"If it is unfinished when he returns, that hut is to be given to someone "
"else, or it is to be demolished and rebuilt."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.35"
msgid ""
"No ce aññassa vā dadeyya bhinditvā vā puna kāreyya, āpatti dvinnaṃ "
"dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"If he does not give it to someone else, or does not demolish and rebuild it, "
"he commits two offenses of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.36"
msgid "sārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where harm will be done, but which has a space on all sides, he commits one "
"offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.37"
msgid "anārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, but which lacks a space on all sides, he commits "
"one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.38"
msgid "anārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, anāpatti."
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides, there is no "
"offense."

#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="87"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1503"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.39"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.40"
msgid "“kuṭiṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a hut and then departs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.41"
msgid ""
"Tassa kuṭiṃ karonti adesi­ta­vatthu­kaṃ pamā­ṇātik­kantaṃ sārambhaṃ "
"aparikkamanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They build one whose site has not been approved, which exceeds the size "
"limit, where harm will be done, and which lacks a space on all sides."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.42"
msgid ""
"So ce vippakate āgacchati, tena bhikkhunā sā kuṭi aññassa vā dātabbā "
"bhinditvā vā puna kātabbā."
msgstr ""
"If it is unfinished when he returns, that hut is to be given to someone "
"else, or it is to be demolished and rebuilt."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.43"
msgid ""
"No ce aññassa vā dadeyya bhinditvā vā puna kāreyya, āpatti dvinnaṃ "
"saṃghādisesena dvinnaṃ dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"If he does not give it to someone else, or does not demolish and rebuild it, "
"he commits two offenses entailing suspension and two offenses of wrong "
"conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.44"
msgid ""
"sārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti dvinnaṃ saṃghādisesena dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where harm will be done, but which has a space on all sides, he commits two "
"offense entailing suspension and one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.45"
msgid ""
"anārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti dvinnaṃ saṃghādisesena dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, but which lacks a space on all sides, he commits "
"two offenses entailing suspension and one offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.46"
msgid "anārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti dvinnaṃ saṃ­ghādi­sesānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides, he commits "
"two offenses entailing suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="88"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1504"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.47"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.48"
msgid "“kuṭiṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a hut and then departs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.49"
msgid ""
"Tassa kuṭiṃ karonti desita­vatthu­kaṃ pamāṇikaṃ sārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"They build one whose site has been approved, which is within the size limit, "
"where harm will be done, and which lacks a space on all sides."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.50"
msgid ""
"So ce vippakate āgacchati, tena bhikkhunā sā kuṭi aññassa vā dātabbā "
"bhinditvā vā puna kātabbā."
msgstr ""
"If it is unfinished when he returns, that hut is to be given to someone "
"else, or it is to be demolished and rebuilt."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.51"
msgid ""
"No ce aññassa vā dadeyya bhinditvā vā puna kāreyya, āpatti dvinnaṃ "
"dukkaṭānaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"If he does not give it to someone else, or does not demolish and rebuild it, "
"he commits two offenses of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.52"
msgid "sārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, āpatti dukkaṭassa … pe …"
msgstr ""
"where harm will be done, but which has a space on all sides, he commits one "
"offense of wrong conduct. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.53"
msgid "anārambhaṃ aparikkamanaṃ, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"where no harm will be done, but which lacks a space on all sides, he commits "
"one offense of wrong conduct."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="89"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1505"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.54"
msgid "Bhikkhu samādisitvā pakkamati—"
msgstr "A monk appoints someone"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.55"
msgid "“kuṭiṃ me karothā”ti."
msgstr "to build him a hut and then departs."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.14.56"
msgid ""
"Tassa kuṭiṃ karonti desita­vatthu­kaṃ pamāṇikaṃ anārambhaṃ saparikkamanaṃ, "
"anāpatti."
msgstr ""
"They build one whose site has been approved, which is within the size limit, "
"where no harm will be done, and which has a space on all sides, there is no "
"offense."

#. </p><h3>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.15.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Permutations part 2"

#. </h3><p><a class="sc" id="90"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.6.3.15"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1506"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.15.1"
msgid "Attanā vippakataṃ attanā pariyosāpeti, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"If he finishes what he began himself, he commits an offense entailing "
"suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="91"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1507"></a> 
#. VAR: pariyosāpeti → pariyosāvāpeti (mr)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.15.2"
msgid "Attanā vippakataṃ parehi pariyosāpeti, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"If he gets others to finish what he began himself, he commits an offense "
"entailing suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="92"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1508"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.15.3"
msgid "Parehi vippakataṃ attanā pariyosāpeti, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"If he finishes himself what was begun by others, he commits an offense "
"entailing suspension."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="93"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1509"></a> 
#. VAR: pariyosāpeti → pariyosāvāpeti (mr)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.15.4"
msgid "Parehi vippakataṃ parehi pariyosāpeti, āpatti saṃ­ghā­di­sesassa."
msgstr ""
"If he gets others to finish what was begun by others, he commits an offense "
"entailing suspension."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.16.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Non-offenses"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="94"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.6.3.16"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1510"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.16.1"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr "There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.16.2"
msgid "leṇe"
msgstr "if it is a shelter;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.16.3"
msgid "guhāya"
msgstr "if it is a cave;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.16.4"
msgid "tiṇakuṭikāya"
msgstr "if it is a grass hut;"

#. <a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.265"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.16.5"
msgid "aññassatthāya vāsāgāraṃ ṭhapetvā"
msgstr "if it is built for someone else;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.16.6"
msgid "sabbattha,"
msgstr "if it is anything apart from a dwelling;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.16.7"
msgid "anāpatti ummattakassa"
msgstr "if he is insane;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.16.8"
msgid "ādi­kammi­kas­sāti."
msgstr "if he is the first offender."

#. </p><hr><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="95"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1511"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss6:pts-cs3.16.9"
msgid "Kuṭikā­ra­sikkhā­padaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr "The sixth rule, the training rule on building huts, is finished."

